    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab><persName><name ref="Sanitulus/Toto">Sanitulo</name>, qui Toto</persName>
                        vocatur, filio <persName>bone memorie <name ref="Adalbaldus"
                                >Adalpaldi</name></persName> riceve da <persName ref="#people/214"
                            key="#Bishops">Gherardus</persName>, gratia Dei huius sancte Lucane
                        ecclesie humilis <rs key="#Bishops">episcopus</rs>, per cartula livellario
                        nomine (…), duo case et res ille massaricie in <placeName ref="#places/2107"
                            >loco Ducentula</placeName> prope <rs key="#Churches">ecclesie</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Churches" ref="#juridical_persons/3302">Sancti
                            Martini</orgName>, quas <persName key="#Agricultural_workers">quondam
                                <name ref="Gaiprandulo">Gheiprandulo</name></persName> et <persName
                            key="#Agricultural_workers"><name ref="Bonaldulus"
                            >Bonaldulo</name></persName> ad manus suas abuerunt, et sunt pertinentes
                        ipsius <rs key="#Mother_churches">episcopatui</rs> vestro <orgName
                            key="#Mother_churches" ref="#juridical_persons/68">Sancti
                            Martini</orgName>; casa vero ipsa una cum terris, vineis, silvis,
                        virgareis, pratis, pascuis, cultas res vel incultas, omnia quantum ad ipse
                        case est pertinentes et suprascripsti <rs key="#Agricultural_workers"
                            >massarii</rs> exinde ad manus suas abuerunt in integrum mihi eas
                        dedisti tali ordinem ut da admodum in mea vel de meis heredes sint
                        potestatem eas abendi, imperandi, laborare faciendi, meliorandi et nobis eos
                        privato nomine usufructuandi. Censo: (…) pro omni censum et iustitja exinde
                        tibi vel ad subcessoribus tuis per singulos annos, per omnem mense magio,
                        dare debeamus hic Luca ad ipso <rs key="#Domus">domu</rs> episcopatui vestro
                        Sancti Martini, per nos aut per misso nostro, vobis vel ad ministeriale
                        vestro argentum denarios bonos expendiviles numero triginta; et homines
                        illos qui in ipse casis abitantes fuerit nos eos a mandato vestro venire
                        faciamus hic Luca legem et iustitjam faciendum tantum (…). Pena: spondeo ego
                        (…) una cum meis heredes conponere tibi (…) penam argentum soledos
                        quinquaginta (…). <persName key="#Writer #Witness #Notary"><name ref="Leo"
                                >Leo</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs> scrive due <rs
                            key="#Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis">cartulas</rs>. Actum <placeName
                            ref="#places/4" key="#Domus #Churches #Mother_churches #Bishops"
                            >Luca</placeName>.</ab>
                    <ab>Sottoscrivono come <rs key="#Witness">testimoni</rs>: <persName
                            key="#Witness #Notary"><name ref="Adalbertus"
                            >Adalpertus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs>, <persName key="#Scabini"><name
                                ref="Benedictus">Benedicto</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Scabini">schabinus</rs>, <persName key="#Witness"><name
                                ref="Iohannes">Iohannes</name></persName>, <persName
                            key="#Witness #Notary"><name ref="Georgius">Georgius</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs>, <persName key="#Witness" ref="#people/150"
                            >Fraolmi</persName>, <persName key="#Witness #Notary"><name ref="Petrus"
                                >Petrus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs>,</ab>
                </div>
            </div>
